Uh, I told Beckman
that I'm out.

38:44.234 --> 38:47.401
I mean, after all, I did
get her her job back, and

38:47.467 --> 38:49.434
simultaneously saved
multiple branches

38:49.501 --> 38:51.601
of the United States government,
so she accepted.

38:51.668 --> 38:54.067
I'm a civilian
just like you.

38:54.134 --> 38:56.067
Really?

38:56.134 --> 38:57.366
You were right, sis.

38:57.367 --> 38:59.267
There's nothing more important
than family.

39:02.034 --> 39:03.732
Love you.

39:03.733 --> 39:05.867
I love you, too.

39:34.934 --> 39:37.034
Oh, boy.

39:45.733 --> 39:47.934
Hello, Chuck.

39:48.000 --> 39:49.633
If you're seeing this,

39:49.634 --> 39:52.634
that means I wasn't able to stop
this message from sending.

39:52.700 --> 39:56.000
which also means I'm dead.

39:56.067 --> 39:59.800
I want to say about that, um,

39:59.867 --> 40:01.867
I- I'm sorry and-and...

40:03.634 --> 40:07.201
Well, I hope you and your sister
know how much I love you.

40:09.833 --> 40:12.401
Loved you.

40:12.467 --> 40:15.467
Now I need you
to do something for me,

40:15.534 --> 40:16.766
Charles.

40:16.767 --> 40:17.933
Something secret.

40:17.934 --> 40:19.834
You better get a pen.

40:22.434 --> 40:25.167
<i>I never wanted you
to be a spy.</i>

40:25.234 --> 40:27.334
<i>I knew how dangerous
this world is,</i>

40:27.401 --> 40:29.967
<i>what it does
to the people in it.</i>

40:30.034 --> 40:32.767
<i>Boy, do I know that.</i>

40:32.833 --> 40:36.601
<i>That's why I kept something
from you,</i>

40:36.668 --> 40:40.000
<i>something about me,
about Orion.</i>

40:40.067 --> 40:42.100
Charles, I'll be back
in a second.

40:42.167 --> 40:44.067
Hey, Dad.

40:50.067 --> 40:53.167
<i>I've been a spy
for the last 20 years,</i>

40:53.234 --> 40:55.167
<i>working for myself,</i>

40:55.234 --> 40:59.134
<i>doing things
governments are afraid to do.</i>

41:06.867 --> 41:09.100
<i>Maybe being a spy is...</i>

41:09.167 --> 41:11.234
<i>is in our blood,</i>

41:11.301 --> 41:14.301
<i>and... maybe
I should have told you...</i>

41:14.367 --> 41:16.334
<i>all of this long ago,</i>

41:16.401 --> 41:18.601
<i>but</i>

41:18.668 --> 41:20.601
<i>Chuck,</i>

41:20.668 --> 41:23.833
<i>your story-
it's only just beginning.</i>

41:26.234 --> 41:29.000
<i>It's time you know the truth
about my work</i>

41:29.067 --> 41:32.767
<i>and about the people
who tried to destroy me</i>

41:32.833 --> 41:34.633
<i>because if I'm gone,</i>

41:34.634 --> 41:37.800
<i>then you're not safe
from them anymore,</i>

41:37.867 --> 41:40.767
<i>and neither is Ellie.</i>

41:42.067 --> 41:44.134
<i>These people-
they-they are...</i>

41:44.201 --> 41:48.534
<i>They are ruthless
and cunning and...</i>

41:51.134 --> 41:53.034
<i>Chuck, it's-it's time
you learned</i>

41:53.100 --> 41:55.000
<i>about your family.</i>

41:58.867 --> 42:00.833
<i>Because...</i>

42:02.467 --> 42:05.334
<i>I did it all for her.</i>

